    Large epidemic simulated serosurvey

    simdata_large_epi.Rd

    Simulated dataset describing a large epidemic between the years 2032 and 2035 with a constant force-of-infection with value 1.5. The hypothetical serosurvey is conducted in year 2050 for 250 individuals that are up to 50 years old.

    simdata_large_epi

    Format

    An object of class "cross"; see qtl::read.cross().

    Examples

    simdata_large_epi
#>               survey total counts age_min age_max tsur country      test
